quran[16{c,v,t}:
36,55,aaj janati log mazay karne mein mashgool hain
36,56,woh aur un ki biwiyan ghany saayon mein hain masnadon par takiye lagaye hue
36,57,"har qisam ki lazeez cheeze khanay peenay ko un ke liye wahan mojood hain, jo kuch woh talab karen unn ke liye haazir hai"
36,58,rab Raheem ki taraf se un ko salam kaha gaya hai
36,59,"aur ae mujrimo, aaj tum chaatt kar allag ho jao"
36,60,"aadam ke bachcho, kya mein ne tum ko hadaayat nah ki thi ke shetan ki bandagi nah karo, woh tumhara khula dushman hai"
36,61,"aur meri hi bandagi karo, yeh seedha rasta hai ?"
36,62,magar is ke bawajood is ne tum mein se aik giroh kaseer ko gumraah kar diya kya tum aqal nahi rakhtay thay ?
36,63,yeh wohi jahannum hai jis se tum ko daraya jata raha tha
36,64,jo kufar tum duniya mein karte rahay ho uss ki Padaash mein ab iss ka eendhan bano
36,65,"aaj hum inn ke mun band kiye dete hain, inn ke haath hum se bolein ge aur un ke paon gawahi den ge ke yeh duniya mein kya kamaai karte rahay hain"
36,66,"hum chahain to inn ki ankhen moond den, phir yeh rastay ki taraf lapak kar dekhen, kahan se aِnhin rasta sujhai day ga ?"
36,67,hum chahain to aِnhin inn ki jagah hi par is terhan maskh kar ke rakh den ke yeh nah agay chal saken nah peechay palat saken
36,68,"jis shakhs ko hum lambi Umar dete hain is ki saakht ko hum ulat hi dete hain, kya ( yeh halaat dekh kar ) inhen aqal nahi aati ?"
36,69,hum ne iss ( nabi ) ko shair nahi sikhaya hai aur nah shairi is ko Zaib hi deti hai yeh to aik nasiyaat hai aur saaf parhi jaane wali kitaab
36,70,taakay woh har uss shakhs ko khabardaar kar day jo zindah ho aur inkaar karne walon par Hujjat qaim ho jaye
